---
description: Solid frontend boundaries for Replyline
globs:
  - src/app/**
alwaysApply: false
---

- Keep frontend state/types in `src/app/model.ts`.
- Keep orchestration logic in `src/app/controller.ts` (do not move into component files).
- Keep platform bridge usage in `src/app/platform.ts`.
- Keep UI reactivity in Solid.js patterns, not React patterns.
- Preserve RU-first UX with EN mirror for user-facing behavior.
- Add/update tests with behavior changes (`*.test.ts`, `*.ui.test.tsx`).